32:50.369 --> 32:51.470
Horse.

32:52.204 --> 32:54.106
(BEEP)

32:54.173 --> 32:56.475
This is a...

32:58.744 --> 33:00.779
Lana, what do you
see here?

33:04.216 --> 33:05.651
We need you
to keep talking to us.

33:08.054 --> 33:09.321
Have we already
done damage?

33:09.388 --> 33:11.257
It's too soon, I think.

33:11.323 --> 33:12.924
We need to stop.

33:12.991 --> 33:16.128
If we leave the AVM
intact and it ruptures,
it will kill her.

33:23.769 --> 33:25.237
Lana,
do you understand?

33:26.738 --> 33:29.041
I have to keep going,
but if you stop talking,

33:29.108 --> 33:30.576
you may never
talk again.

33:30.642 --> 33:33.079
**

33:40.018 --> 33:41.687
Hand me
the bipolar forceps.

33:42.654 --> 33:43.955
Dr. Lim.

33:44.022 --> 33:46.192
There's a Javi Maldonado
insisting he should
be in here.

33:46.258 --> 33:48.627
**

34:07.045 --> 34:08.480
(DOOR OPENS)

34:08.547 --> 34:10.249
I'm sorry
to keep you waiting.

34:10.316 --> 34:12.251
The surgery
was a success.

34:12.318 --> 34:13.719
You can see her
when she wakes up.

34:17.022 --> 34:18.157
Thank you.

34:32.738 --> 34:34.473
She wasn't great
with you,

34:34.540 --> 34:36.675
but she's great
with Teresa.

34:36.742 --> 34:39.578
That doesn't mean
she loves her more than you.

34:39.645 --> 34:41.980
It may just mean...

34:42.047 --> 34:44.616
She's not the same
person anymore.

34:44.683 --> 34:47.052
As soon as she saw me,
she started giving me crap.

34:48.053 --> 34:49.255
The same crap.

34:51.557 --> 34:54.326
Actually, the first thing
she said was...

34:56.228 --> 34:57.529
...you look pretty.

34:58.230 --> 35:00.832
**

35:19.418 --> 35:22.154
Lana, what's on
the screen?

35:22.221 --> 35:23.689
A lion.

35:27.226 --> 35:28.260
(BEEP)

35:30.862 --> 35:32.063
And what is that?

35:35.901 --> 35:37.603
Lana, what's on
the screen?

35:46.478 --> 35:47.646
Javi...

35:57.723 --> 35:59.725
Madagascan
Hissing Cockroach.

36:05.764 --> 36:08.900
Gromphadorhina
portentosa.

36:10.636 --> 36:14.506
One of the few insects

36:14.573 --> 36:17.243
who give birth
to live young,

36:17.309 --> 36:19.177
rather than laying eggs.

36:20.479 --> 36:22.648
Keep going.
You both are doing great.

36:22.714 --> 36:24.383
**

36:24.450 --> 36:28.254
Long-tailed
South African Scorpion.

36:28.320 --> 36:31.257
Hadogenes
troglodytes.

36:31.323 --> 36:33.692
Reaches a length
of over eight inches,

36:33.759 --> 36:35.694
the longest scorpion
in the world.

36:39.331 --> 36:41.267
You'll still need to fly
to China to get checked out,

36:41.333 --> 36:42.768
but everything
looks great.

36:42.834 --> 36:44.169
SUNNY: Thank you.

36:49.841 --> 36:51.977
Mom,
Grace is outside.

36:56.848 --> 36:58.116
I think you should
talk to her.

36:58.183 --> 36:59.451
Why?

37:00.218 --> 37:02.288
Because...

37:02.354 --> 37:03.355
She's your daughter.

37:11.029 --> 37:12.564
I'll step out.
It's okay.

37:17.869 --> 37:18.870
Mom.

37:20.806 --> 37:22.308
Since we
stopped talking,

37:22.374 --> 37:24.810
there hasn't been a day
I haven't thought about you.

37:26.177 --> 37:27.746
That I haven't
missed you.

37:27.813 --> 37:30.181
**

37:31.583 --> 37:33.919
(VOICE BREAKING)
I'm sorry.

37:33.985 --> 37:35.521
For everything.

37:48.567 --> 37:49.835
I sat in the back.

37:53.372 --> 37:55.173
At the Troubadour.

37:55.240 --> 37:58.777
You were singing
I Wish It Would Rain
with that band.

38:04.950 --> 38:06.284
I cried.

38:07.853 --> 38:09.521
It was beautiful.

38:20.532 --> 38:22.233
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

38:22.300 --> 38:25.371
**

38:48.259 --> 38:49.995
(MONITORS BEEPING)

38:50.061 --> 38:52.263
**

38:55.667 --> 38:57.168
DR. REZNICK:
Can you tell me
your name?

39:02.574 --> 39:04.275
You remember
your name?

39:10.181 --> 39:13.519
Of course I remember
my name...

39:13.585 --> 39:16.087
Lana.

39:16.154 --> 39:19.090
And you're Javi.

39:25.163 --> 39:26.698
I think I love you.

39:28.333 --> 39:30.101
I think you do, too.

39:37.208 --> 39:40.479
Do you want to
stay in bed with me
after we have sex?

39:43.281 --> 39:44.282
No.

39:57.996 --> 40:00.365
**

40:05.671 --> 40:07.506
(DISTANT GIGGLING)

40:33.031 --> 40:36.968
(AG AND BRIAN FENNELL'S
NO EXPECTATIONS PLAYS)

40:37.035 --> 40:41.439
**

40:57.088 --> 40:59.124
Dr. Glassman?

41:01.760 --> 41:03.729
Dr. Glassman?

41:03.795 --> 41:06.064
**

41:07.599 --> 41:09.034
I'm not here to help.

41:21.246 --> 41:25.216
* Take me to the station

41:26.384 --> 41:30.288
* And put me on the train

41:31.623 --> 41:36.161
* I got no expectations

41:37.295 --> 41:41.266
* To pass through here again

41:42.734 --> 41:47.739
* Once I was a rich man

41:47.806 --> 41:53.244
* Now I am so poor

41:53.311 --> 41:59.084
* But never in my
sweet, short life

41:59.150 --> 42:03.021
* Have I felt
like this before *

42:03.088 --> 42:04.089
(WEAKLY) Thank you.

42:09.360 --> 42:12.197
**

42:24.776 --> 42:26.778
**
